Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.44,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}In this room filled with light,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.44,0:00:48.98,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I'll be waiting for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:07.67,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}If you'd realize you're floating and gazing upon a box,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:12.80,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}You'd notice it doesn't return your gaze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:19.43,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}The reflected heart is pure white
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:25.56,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Just like the light from the falling snow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.14,0:01:30.98,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}This shivering rain that blankets me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.98,0:01:37.91,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Isn't going to dispel until the spring breeze returns
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:41.37,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}So let's search for some azalea
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:45.54,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Bring me with you to a comforting garden
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:48.58,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Is not something I can ask
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:55.76,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}That fairy tale-like happiness isn't real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.59,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I know that much already
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.43,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}But still
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:04.89,Yahari OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I want to go there
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:21.44,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Shining in the bright blue sky I hate so
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:28.53,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}An airplane soars toward the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:36.54,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Something is stirring from within my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.00,0:22:41.21,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I keep all the things I want to say pent up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.71,0:22:48.22,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And turn them into things I can no longer say
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.99,0:22:56.39,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I can't even be honest until the end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:23:03.11,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Just forget that I wanted to be with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.32,0:23:06.44,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}And that I set you free
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.44,0:23:13.33,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}If I had told you I wanted to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.70,0:23:17.79,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Before the faint trail you left behind vanished,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:23.04,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I would be freed from this
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.04,0:23:26.63,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Heartbreak that never ends
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:30.97,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}I could be here with you again
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:36.51,Yahari ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)}Hello! Hello! Alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's been a week since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:22.46,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence that I saved your dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:25.96,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'd probably still be alone even if the accident never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.28,0:00:28.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If you're being kind because you're worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.30,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,then stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.91,0:00:33.05,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,How did things end up this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.72,0:00:35.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Idiot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.71,0:00:40.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Sabure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:20.72,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:26.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Sup.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.32,0:02:27.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}H-Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.83,0:02:38.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay. Smooth. Things are completely reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:44.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,My heart is at ease once again because our relationship has been reset.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:47.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama has been freed from her guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.17,0:02:49.96,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She has returned to her normal life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.96,0:02:52.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Considering my options, it wasn't the wrong decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:54.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,No, it was the correct choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's why it ended with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:03:00.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's fine if we just return to our normal daily routines again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:05.99,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,While you can't reset your life, you can reset your relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.99,0:03:07.47,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The source is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:10.56,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Not a single one of my middle school classmates has contacted—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That wasn't a reset. It was deletion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:18.72,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Did something happen between you and Yuigahama?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:20.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nope. Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:24.22,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If nothing happened, I doubt she would stop coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:26.11,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Did you have a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:29.04,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:35.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Moreover, fights only happen between people close to one another, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:37.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So rather than a fight—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.31,0:03:38.90,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,A dispute?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:40.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Did you think that was closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.31,0:03:42.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Then war?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Wrong. You're getting colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,An extermination.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.20,0:03:47.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Were you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.70,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Colder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.12,0:03:51.71,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,A disagreement, I suppose?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.47,0:03:53.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:54.54,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:56.00,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nothing to be done then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:00.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What, no Yuigahama today either?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.65,0:04:02.71,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Please knock, Ms. Hiratsuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:05.72,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Darn, and here I had some expectations for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:10.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Um, did you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:12.60,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.61,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Let's change the match from before into a battle royale.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.05,0:04:18.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,A battle royale with just two people?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.22,0:04:22.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You can recruit new members if you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:24.78,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Since it seems like Yuigahama won't be showing up anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's not like Yuigahama has quit—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:28.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If she doesn't come, it's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:31.58,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Worrying about people with no motivation beyond compulsory education is moot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:33.49,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Those without the will can leave if they want to.{意志なき者は去るほかない}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.47,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:40.41,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I have no motivation or will, so can I leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.35,0:04:43.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:51.52,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks to Yuigahama, we know that club growth is tied to club activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.80,0:04:53.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,This is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.35,0:05:01.03,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Find at least one new member who is motivated and has the will by Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, you can start now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:08.41,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Tyrant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.28,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.98,0:05:12.37,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm trying to be nice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hiratsuka, I'd like to confirm something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:17.62,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,We're supposed to look for new members, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.62,0:05:19.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Exactly, Yukinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.01,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I wish you luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:27.59,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,New members, huh? What're we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:30.37,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I already know someone who may join.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:31.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Who? Totsuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.28,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Totsuka, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be Totsuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:35.48,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:36.22,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.03,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I mean, she quit, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Then she can just join again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.09,0:05:45.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Ms. Hiratsuka only said to find new members.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:47.78,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You think she'll rejoin that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.03,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's pretty normal for people who leave to not come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:53.66,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,June 18th. Do you know what that day is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.53,0:05:55.16,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.60,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's Yuigahama's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:05:58.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Her email address had 0618 in it, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:03.69,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So you haven't asked her directly, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.54,0:06:06.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's quite the power of communication you've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:12.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I want to celebrate her birthday with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:15.56,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So even if Yuigahama doesn't come back to the Volunteers Club,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:19.13,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I want her to know that I'm thankful for all she's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:19.73,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Say, Hikigaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.41,0:06:26.53,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, u-um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:30.93,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Would you like to go out, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:42.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you tag along on your day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.67,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,No probs! I wanna buy Yui a birthday present too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:48.93,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And I'm looking forward to spending the day with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,All right, let's do this as efficiently as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:52.82,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'll head this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.03,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'll take the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.72,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Then Komachi can take this dir—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:58.06,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:01.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What the...? My finger really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.11,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Since we're all here, let's just stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.82,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,This way we can ask each other for advice. Better for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:09.99,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But if we do that, we won't be able to check all the stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:10.95,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:14.69,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,According to my professional opinion about Yui's interests...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:19.04,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,We'll be fine as long as we check out this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.49,0:07:29.05,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Komachi, it should be around here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:32.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Did you see where Komachi went?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.31,0:07:35.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Heya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:37.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.81,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's a bunch of stuff I wanna buy. I sort of forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.81,0:07:44.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You were the one who suggested we stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.95,0:07:48.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I can't believe my sister's mind has turned to mush.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.31,0:07:49.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Your big brother's in shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:53.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I guess it's impossible for you to understand why, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:54.52,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.52,0:07:55.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Uh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'll probably be another five hours or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'll go home myself, so you two can fight on together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.97,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Wha? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.97,0:08:07.00,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's no "fighting on" when we're just shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.26,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yukinoshita...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:15.01,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What did Komachi say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.89,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There was some stuff she wanted to buy, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:21.02,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She pushed the rest onto us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She did come with us on her day off,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,so I guess we can't really complain.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.27,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,We'll figure something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.18,0:08:30.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:33.87,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.79,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Am I really {\i1}that{\i0} suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.47,0:08:49.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It appears that in this area, people are cautious of male customers that are alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.80,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I guess even if I'm here, there's not much I can do to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:54.72,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'll head over in that direc—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:55.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:08:59.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Do you intend to leave this to my discretion?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:04.56,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm not bragging, but my standards are different than normal high school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.69,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,At least you understand that about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:10.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:12.49,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'd like it if you helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.07,0:09:16.91,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,While I've experienced a crushing failure giving a presentation to a girl before,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I've never bought a present or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.19,0:09:21.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't think I can really go into any stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.61,0:09:24.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's no helping it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.17,0:09:26.39,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Try not to wander too far away from me then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:27.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Too far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You can't understand without me spelling it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.44,0:09:34.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If all you can do is breathe in and out, then even an AC unit is more useful than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:38.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,True. It would be so much easier if I had a feature that could read the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:42.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,In other words, until the end of today,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.87,0:09:46.56,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm saying it's okay if we act like lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:50.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Quite the high horse you're on there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:51.33,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Displeased with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.33,0:09:53.19,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.78,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:58.37,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's nothing to be surprised about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:02.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The last thing I'd want is to be her boyfriend, but she doesn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.77,0:10:05.00,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She said act, so it'll definitely be acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.00,0:10:06.71,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So there's no misunderstandings here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.29,0:10:09.67,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You definitely have a problem with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.67,0:10:12.30,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Not really. There's no real reason for me to refuse either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.30,0:10:14.21,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Actually, shouldn't you be the one refusing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:16.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I don't really mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:18.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If there are only strangers around,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.42,0:10:21.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,there's no need to worry about financial damage due to a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Things can't go on like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:35.33,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I guess we really do need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.10,0:10:38.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I haven't even given him the cookies either.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.14,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,We aren't getting her office supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.14,0:10:48.87,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And if we're picking clothes for their durability, we'll never decide on what to get.{耐久性とかで服を選んでたら\N一生 決まんないと思うぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.23,0:10:52.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I doubt she wears clothes for their defensive capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.50,0:10:55.27,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What other choice was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.27,0:10:58.13,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I can only make a decision based on the material and stitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:11:05.14,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I don't know what sort of things she likes, or what her hobbies are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.45,0:11:07.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Does it matter if you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.32,0:11:11.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Actually, it annoys me when someone says they "know" something with inadequate information.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:15.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's like sending peas from somewhere else to someone from Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:17.53,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That example was so specific to Chiba. I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.89,0:11:21.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's like sending wine to a sommelier with only basic knowledge about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:24.24,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I see now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:26.37,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:29.12,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:33.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask me how it looks, all I can say is that it really suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.64,0:11:35.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.68,0:11:37.67,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But we aren't talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:40.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I was asking what you thought about it for Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:46.35,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't she be happier with something fluffier and more colorful for someone lacking in the brain department?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.89,0:11:50.89,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That was pretty harsh, but it's hard to respond because it's so accurate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'll go with this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:54.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's fine. Whatever you pick works.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.42,0:11:56.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You're buying that one too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:00.53,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is that you, Yukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:05.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It is Yukino.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:08.27,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.27,0:12:09.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:20.71,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm Yukino's older sister, Haruno.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.04,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.04,0:12:24.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hikigaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.25,0:12:26.43,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hikigaya...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:31.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hikigaya, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.76,0:12:33.39,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Well, nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}When did you two start going out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:38.30,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Come on, out with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.30,0:12:40.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We're just classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.09,0:12:42.53,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm not her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.10,0:12:45.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No reason to get flustered about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.25,0:12:49.03,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I won't forgive you if you make her cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.03,0:12:49.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,H-Hold—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.92,0:12:50.48,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:52.27,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So close! Too close! Close!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:53.66,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But she {\i1}does{\i0} smell good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:55.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Could you please give it a rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.61,0:13:00.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I guess I got a bit carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.66,0:13:06.09,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She's a bit delicate, so look out for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:12.02,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Did I do something you don't like just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.24,0:13:14.25,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I have sensitive ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.88,0:13:20.15,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hikigaya, stop exposing your fetishes to a woman you just met.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You won't have any recourse even if you get sued.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.60,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You're so interesting, Hikigaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:28.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:31.79,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any more business with us, we'll be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.54,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hikigaya, let's have tea after you become her boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Your sister {\i1}sure{\i0} is something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:43.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Everyone who meets her says the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:47.03,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone else as perfect as her, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:49.21,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Everyone praises her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.30,0:13:52.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You aren't all that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.76,0:13:54.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Roundabout boasting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:58.43,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,When I said "something," I meant... uh, how should I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:01.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,How she puts up that thick facade.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:04.91,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She's sociable, and is always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.99,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,She's even nice when talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Certainly, she's every man's ideal woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:13.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But that's just an ideal. It's not real.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.08,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's why something seems fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.08,0:14:17.00,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Despite your rotten eyes—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:20.26,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,No, {\i1}because{\i0} of them you're able to see through some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.26,0:14:21.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to be a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.69,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}is{\i0} a compliment. I'm praising you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.60,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,A-A dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:39.02,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,H-Hikigaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:42.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:45.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's your owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:49.66,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,No leash?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What's with this dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.77,0:14:55.12,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Isn't it a little too friendly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:58.54,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,This dog...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:14:59.75,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.09,0:15:02.38,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry about my dog bothering—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:05.15,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:05.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.69,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hikki and Yukinon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:10.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Why are you together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.60,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Why? No reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.20,0:15:12.60,Yahai main alt,,0,0,0,,Why? No reason.{said together}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.36,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:16.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Forget about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.44,0:15:19.89,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's obvious what it means when you're out together on your day off, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:22.78,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.78,0:15:25.22,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,How did I not notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.22,0:15:27.07,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And I'm supposed to be good at reading the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:32.11,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Is she misunderstanding something weird here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.40,0:15:35.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I'm gonna leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:39.39,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama, we need to have a talk about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.39,0:15:42.17,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Could you come to the club room on Monday?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:46.88,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I don't think I'll want to hear it though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.88,0:15:50.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's no point in telling me now either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.32,0:15:52.34,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can really do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:57.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I couldn't really tell you properly because of how I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:00.48,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,but I want to talk this through with you properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:01.80,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:20.16,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.83,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hi-Hikki?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.02,0:16:25.11,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What is it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.11,0:16:26.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The air sure is nice out here.{vale halp make this joke work: 空気が おいしかったというか…}{Oh my god, this is genius}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:32.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,C'mon. Let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.49,0:16:36.47,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:39.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Ya-Yahello, Yukinon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.38,0:16:46.36,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:54.31,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,S-So you wanted to talk about you and Hikki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:54.86,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.77,0:16:58.38,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to you about our future—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.38,0:17:02.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to trouble yourself with me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:04.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I mean, sure, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:06.96,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But I actually feel like I should celebrate now instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I want to properly celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:13.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And besides, I'm really grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.74,0:17:15.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I dunno about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.37,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything for you to be grateful about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.37,0:17:19.51,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.96,0:17:23.27,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, I'm grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:28.84,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Moreover, celebrating isn't something you do just because the person did something, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:31.01,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I just genuinely want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,O-Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.63,0:17:35.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It seems like they're having two different conversations here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.30,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,S-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:40.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I don't think I want to hear any more...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:43.62,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama, aren't you misunderstanding something here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:45.89,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.89,0:17:48.79,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Then you two {\i1}aren't{\i0} going out or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.15,0:17:50.63,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama, even {\i1}I{\i0} have things that make me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.74,0:17:59.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,There's no way that guy could be in a relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,He can't even maintain normal relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.50,0:18:02.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Shove off.{lit: leave me/it alone}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.42,0:18:04.54,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Like I'd bother with something as annoying as relationships.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:06.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If I got a phone call in the dead of the night with someone crying on the other end,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:08.59,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I'm confident I'd break up with them on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:13.77,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry. Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I guess we don't have any time for the celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.94,0:18:19.66,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And I even baked a cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:21.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,A cake? Why a cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.92,0:18:23.13,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.13,0:18:26.62,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I called you here today to celebrate your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.62,0:18:27.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:33.30,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You haven't been coming to the club lately, so I wanted to show my appreciation for what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:37.63,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I suppose this is what you'd call a "token of gratitude."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.36,0:18:39.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You got me a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:43.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:46.71,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I wasn't the only one who got you something though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:53.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I never would've expected Hikki to give me a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.41,0:18:57.55,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Things have been a little awkward because of what happened before and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.32,0:19:01.70,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Sorry, this isn't just for your birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.73,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,How do I put it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.73,0:19:06.05,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Let's just say this makes us even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.05,0:19:11.46,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,The fact that I saved your dog, and that you looked out for me... is all behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:16.64,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's not like I helped you out of obligation,{そもそも 俺が個人を特定して\N恩を売ったわけじゃないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:20.22,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,so there's no need for you to repay me.{お前が個人を特定して\N恩を返す必要なんてないんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:22.93,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Well, it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:25.35,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I want to repay you for looking out for me at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:27.89,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And with this, it's back to zero. We're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:30.34,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You don't have to worry about me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:32.18,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So that's why it ends with this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.92,0:19:38.10,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Why do you think of it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:43.65,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I've never once thought of it like I'm pitying you or watching out for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:45.85,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:51.50,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's so complicated, I don't really understand anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.33,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I thought it was simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.92,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,It's not so complicated, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:20:00.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hikigaya doesn't believe he helped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.94,0:20:04.09,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,And you don't believe it was because of pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.68,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Things were already wrong from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.68,0:20:12.48,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So I think Hikigaya's decision was right when he said, "It ends with this."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.94,0:20:17.44,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,But I don't want it to end like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.07,0:20:19.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:22.08,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If it's the end, you just need to start again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:23.61,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Neither of you are to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:29.94,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Even if who did the helping and who was being helped varied,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.94,0:20:31.76,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,you both suffered equally, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.76,0:20:35.00,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Then you should blame the source of all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:40.05,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,If neither of you are to blame, there's no reason to disagree.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:45.05,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,So you two should be able to properly start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:52.99,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Ah, I have to go report to Ms. Hiratsuka that we've managed to find a new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:05.12,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I open that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:06.80,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.15,0:21:15.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey, does it look good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.05,0:21:18.62,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:19.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:22.42,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,a dog collar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.43,0:21:26.05,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Tell me that sooner, dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.33,0:21:29.40,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Honestly! I'm going to see Ms. Hiratsuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.62,0:21:32.63,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Thanks, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:45.80,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hikigaya, I have an urgent message for you about the Volunteers Club's summer activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.80,0:23:47.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Please respond as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.74,0:23:50.32,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Are you still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.32,0:23:53.57,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,I've sent you several messages and have been calling for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.57,0:23:56.14,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,You've actually seen them, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.14,0:23:58.29,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you have, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:02.98,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Scary. Super frightening.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.63,0:24:04.74,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:09.20,Yahari main,,0,0,0,,In any case, it's strange not to take a break during summer vacation.
